    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278190/extras/34912fc4f21ac6bae05454970e037157.avif?t=1758646803\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278190/extras_big/34912fc4f21ac6bae05454970e037157.avif?t=1758646803 width=800 height=111 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278190/extras/6ba42d4a277d121bf4f7064b1dc25fe4.avif?t=1758646803\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278190/extras_big/6ba42d4a277d121bf4f7064b1dc25fe4.avif?t=1758646803 width=800 height=167 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278190/extras/0b392a1c14e64a6970ac613527f9c00b.avif?t=1758646803\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278190/extras_big/0b392a1c14e64a6970ac613527f9c00b.avif?t=1758646803 width=800 height=286 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278190/extras/d850525656718e3a319efa61656c3b57.avif?t=1758646803\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278190/extras_big/d850525656718e3a319efa61656c3b57.avif?t=1758646803 width=800 height=148 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278190/extras/407f05b39ecce0445e48c8cd3530ab11.poster.avif?t=1758646803\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278190/extras/407f05b39ecce0445e48c8cd3530ab11.webm?t=1758646803\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278190/extras/407f05b39ecce0445e48c8cd3530ab11.mp4?t=1758646803\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Project: AMICA is filled with colorful, eye-popping areas! From striking jungles to the disco fueled cities of Earth's Sector 5. You'll revisit old areas through branching paths with new weapons and power ups collected along your journey, allowing you to progress further in the world of Project: AMICA.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every weapon has a secondary alt-fire, designed to be just as useful as your primary-fire. Using different types of weapons with their accompanied alt-fire in different combat scenarios will play a big role in your survival. Keeping track of your ammo, health and what power ups you have equipped is key when staying alive and progressing through the areas of Project: AMICA.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278190/extras/876feeccc4c880e679d95cf72fc7dbe0.avif?t=1758646803\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278190/extras_big/876feeccc4c880e679d95cf72fc7dbe0.avif?t=1758646803 width=800 height=148 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In order to realize our vision, we settled for the <strong>GZDoom Engine</strong> as the foundation for Project: AMICA. It not only was <i>the</i> choice for making an old-school FPS game like this, it also allows you to easily modify Project: AMICA however you want with third-party tools!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Project: AMICA is inspired by the games that brought First Person Shooters to where they are today. Games such as Quake, Doom and more! From the start, we at <strong>dofhouse </strong>had two goals in mind, to pay tribute to the &quot;old&quot; and to show the &quot;new&quot; how it's done! <strong>It is our love letter to everything 90's &lt;3</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278190/extras/51bd4ef3b6fe3eac10476b807d4bf582.poster.avif?t=1758646803\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278190/extras/51bd4ef3b6fe3eac10476b807d4bf582.webm?t=1758646803\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278190/extras/51bd4ef3b6fe3eac10476b807d4bf582.mp4?t=1758646803\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Project: AMICA has... </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Old-School Fast Paced Movement &amp; Shooting </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Strafe &amp; Rocket Jumping!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Varied areas with secrets and collectables</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Colorful Old-School Graphics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A wide variety of Power-Ups to collect!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Up-beat Jungle/DnB Soundtrack</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Exciting Boss Battles!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Secrets to find!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mod Support! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>and much much more... (we'll tell you later, let us cook)</i></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game is still in active development!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278190/extras/a43a6f4b125ecd444884c91ea6e48869.poster.avif?t=1758646803\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278190/extras/a43a6f4b125ecd444884c91ea6e48869.webm?t=1758646803\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278190/extras/a43a6f4b125ecd444884c91ea6e48869.mp4?t=1758646803\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
